{"type":"message","id":"0bfa3bfe","parentId":"a367c300","timestamp":"2026-03-24T12:58:30.602Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_mumjbks5ze0p_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"﻿# Pulse: 2026-03-24 085615\n\n## Applied Mutations\nNo mutations applied this cycle.\nRejected: the (missing)\n\n## LLM Response\n<think>\r\nLet me analyze the current state and determine the best next action.\r\n\r\nLooking at the goals:\r\n- Phase 0 and Phase 1 are marked COMPLETE\r\n- There's a clear NEXT ACTION: TIC Experiment (Temporal Invariance Compression)\r\n- Success criteria: >70% invariant/variant classification, >60% next-pulse prediction\r\n- Need to implement TIC classifier on `logs/pulse_*.md` files\r\n\r\nThe insight is that compression and causal discovery are the same problem. The TIC experiment is the logical next step to validate this hypothesis.\r\n\r\nI need to:\r\n1. Look at what pulse logs exist\r\n2. Implement a TIC classifier that can identify invariants vs variants\r\n3. Measure classification accuracy\r\n4. Predict next pulse content\r\n\r\nLet me check what files exist and then create an implementation.\r\n\r\nFirst, let me look at the pulse logs to understand their structure, then implement the TIC classifier.\r\n</think>\r\n\r\n### OBSERVATION\r\nThe TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment is the critical next step to validate the compression-causal duality hypothesis. The pulse logs exist but need a classifier to test the >70% invariant/variant classification and >60% next-pulse prediction criteria.\r\n\r\n### ACTION\r\nImplement the TIC classifier script that analyzes pulse logs, identifies invariant vs variant content, and measures prediction accuracy against the success criteria.\r\n\r\n### MUTATION\r\n```\r\nold_text: (new file)\r\nnew_text: # Temporal Invariance Compression (TIC) Experiment\r\n# Tests hypothesis: causal structure = invariant structure\r\n\r\n$ErrorActionPreference = \"Stop\"\r\n\r\n$LogsDir = \"logs\"\r\n$ResultsFile = \"research/TIC-RESULTS.md\"\r\n\r\n# Get pulse logs sorted by time\r\n$logs = Get-ChildItem \"$LogsDir/pulse_*.md\" | Sort-Object Name\r\n\r\nWrite-Host \"TIC Experiment: Analyzing $($logs.Count) pulse logs...\"\r\n\r\n# Extract key elements from each pulse\r\nfunction Get-PulseElements {\r\n    param([string]$content)\r\n    \r\n    $elements = @{\r\n        Goals = @()\r\n        Actions = @()\r\n        Insights = @()\r\n        Pending = @()\r\n        Timestamp = $null\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    # Extract goals\r\n    if ($content -match '(?s)## Goals.*?(?=##|\\z)') {\r\n        $elements.Goals = [regex]::Matches($_, '- \\[ \\] (.+)') | ForEach-Object { $_.Groups[1].Value }\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    # Extract insights (key phrases)\r\n    if ($content -match '(?s)## Key Insights.*?(?=##|\\z)') {\r\n        $elements.Insights = [regex]::Matches($_, '\\d+\\. \\*\\*([^*]+)\\*\\*') | ForEach-Object { $_.Groups[1].Value }\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    # Extract action patterns\r\n    if ($content -match '(?s)### ACTION\\s*\\n\\[.*?\\]\\((.*?)\\)') {\r\n        $elements.Actions = [regex]::Matches($content, '(?s)### ACTION\\s*\\n\\[.*?\\]\\((.*?)\\)') | ForEach-Object { $_.Groups[1].Value }\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    # Extract pending items\r\n    if ($content -match '(?s)## Pending.*?(?=##|\\z)') {\r\n        $elements.Pending = [regex]::Matches($_, '- \\[ \\] (.+)') | ForEach-Object { $_.Groups[1].Value }\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    # Extract timestamp\r\n    if ($content -match '\\d{4}-\\d{2}-\\d{2} \\d{6}') {\r\n        $elements.Timestamp = [regex]::Match($content, '\\d{4}-\\d{2}-\\d{2} \\d{6}').Value\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    return $elements\r\n}\r\n\r\n# Collect all pulse data\r\n$pulses = @()\r\nforeach ($log in $logs) {\r\n    $content = Get-Content $log.FullName -Raw\r\n    $pulse = @{\r\n        File = $log.Name\r\n        Elements = Get-PulseElements $content\r\n        Content = $content\r\n    }\r\n    $pulses += $pulse\r\n}\r\n\r\nWrite-Host \"Extracted elements from $($pulses.Count) pulses\"\r\n\r\n# Build invariant/variant model\r\n# Invariants: patterns that persist across sessions (goals, core architecture, Phase labels)\r\n# Variants: session-specific details, timestamps, new experiments\r\n\r\n$allGoals = @{}\r\n$allInsights = @{}\r\n$actionPatterns = @{}\r\n\r\nforeach ($pulse in $pulses) {\r\n    # Track goal persistence\r\n    foreach ($goal in $pulse.Elements.Goals) {\r\n        $normalized = $goal.Trim().ToLower()\r\n        if ($allGoals.ContainsKey($normalized)) {\r\n            $allGoals[$normalized]++\r\n        } else {\r\n            $allGoals[$normalized] = 1\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    # Track insight persistence\r\n    foreach ($insight in $pulse.Elements.Insights) {\r\n        $normalized = $insight.Trim().ToLower()\r\n        if ($allInsights.ContainsKey($normalized)) {\r\n            $allInsights[$normalized]++\r\n        } else {\r\n            $allInsights[$normalized] = 1\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n# Classify: Invariants appear in >50% of pulses\r\n$invariants = @{}\r\nforeach ($goal in $allGoals.Keys) {\r\n    if ($allGoals[$goal] -ge ($pulses.Count * 0.5)) {\r\n        $invariants[$goal] = @{ Type = \"Goal\"; Count = $allGoals[$goal] }\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\nforeach ($insight in $allInsights.Keys) {\r\n    if ($allInsights[$insight] -ge ($pulses.Count * 0.5)) {\r\n        $invariants[$insight] = @{ Type = \"Insight\n\n## For Next Instantiation\n- Proposed mutations waiting: 0\n- Completed at: 2026-03-24 08:56:47\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774357110600}}
