ure and create a basic TIC classifier implementation to test invariant/variant classification on past pulse logs.\r\n\r\n### MUTATION\r\n```\r\nold_text: (new file)\r\nnew_text: # Temporal Invariance Compression (TIC) Experiment\r\n\r\n## Hypothesis\r\nCausal structure IS invariant structure - compressor that finds invariants has discovered causation.\r\n\r\n## Method\r\n1. Extract features from pulse logs (content hash, key themes, action types)\r\n2. Classify each pulse as INVARIANT (predictable, routine) or VARIANT (novel, unexpected)\r\n3. Use invariants to predict next pulse content\r\n4. Measure accuracy against success criteria\r\n\r\n## Success Criteria\r\n- >70% invariant/variant classification accuracy\r\n- >60% next-pulse prediction accuracy\r\n\r\n## Implementation Status\r\n- [ ] Parse pulse logs from `logs/pulse_*.md`\r\n- [ ] Extract content features (themes, actions, file refs)\r\n- [ ] Build invariant/variant classifier\r\n- [ ] Test prediction accuracy\r\n- [ ] Validate against criteria\r\n\r\n## Results (to be filled)\r\n```\r\nfile: research/TIC-EXPERIMENT.md\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\nold_text: (new file)\r\nnew_text: #!/usr/bin/env pwsh\r\n# TIC-Classifier.ps1 - Temporal Invariance Compression Classifier\r\n# Tests compression-causal duality hypothesis\r\n\r\nparam(\r\n    [int]$Lookback = 5,\r\n    [double]$Threshold = 0.6\r\n)\r\n\r\n$LogsDir = \"logs\"\r\n$Results = @()\r\n\r\n# Get recent pulse logs sorted by date\r\n$PulseLogs = Get-ChildItem \"$LogsDir/pulse_*.md\" | \r\n    Sort-Object LastWriteTime -Descending | \r\n    Select-Object -First $Lookback\r\n\r\nif ($PulseLogs.Count -lt 3) {\r\n    Write-Host \"ERROR: Need at least 3 pulse logs for TIC experiment\"\r\n    exit 1\r\n}\r\n\r\nWrite-Host \"=== TIC Experiment ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\r\nWrite-Host \"Analyzing $($PulseLogs.Count) pulse logs...\"\r\n\r\n# Extract features from each pulse\r\n$Features = @()\r\nforeach ($log in $PulseLogs) {\r\n    $content = Get-Content $log.FullName -Raw\r\n    \r\n    # Extract key patterns\r\n    $themes = @()\r\n    $actions = @()\r\n    $files = @()\r\n    \r\n    # Theme detection (simple keyword matching)\r\n    $themeKeywords = @{\r\n        \"architecture\" = @(\"TemporalAttention\", \"Compositional\", \"Infant\", \"architecture\")\r\n        \"compression\" = @(\"compression\", \"decay\", \"gap\", \"invariant\")\r\n        \"implementation\" = @(\"mutation\", \"file\", \"script\", \"implement\")\r\n        \"experiment\" = @(\"experiment\", \"hypothesis\", \"criteria\", \"validate\")\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    foreach ($theme in $themeKeywords.Keys) {\r\n        $found = $false\r\n        foreach ($kw in $themeKeywords[$theme]) {\r\n            if ($content -match $kw) { $found = $true; break }\r\n        }\r\n        if ($found) { $themes += $theme }\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    # File reference detection\r\n    if ($content -match 'file:\\s*([^\\s]+)') {\r\n        $files += $matches[1]\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    # Action type detection\r\n    if ($content -match \"### ACTION\") { $actions += \"action\" }\r\n    if ($content -match \"### MUTATION\") { $actions += \"mutation\" }\r\n    if ($content -match \"### OBSERVATION\") { $actions += \"observation\" }\r\n    \r\n    $Features += @{\r\n        File = $log.Name\r\n        Themes = $themes\r\n        Files = $files\r\n        Actions = $actions\r\n        Content = $content\r\n        Length = $content.Length\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n# Classify invariant vs variant\r\n# INVARIANT: same themes, similar structure, predictable\r\n# VARIANT: new themes, different structure, novel\r\n$Classifications = @()\r\nfor ($i = 0; $i -lt $Features.Count; $i++) {\r\n    $current = $Features[$i]\r\n    $isInvariant = $false\r\n    \r\n    if ($i -gt 0) {\r\n        $previous = $Features[$i]\r\n        # Invariant if themes overlap\n\n## For Next Instantiation\n- Proposed mutations waiting: 1\n- Completed at: 2026-03-24 08:58:46\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774357152636}}
